react-text -->\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>not be an affiliate (i.e. a subsidiary, parent, or under common control) of the entity providing the introduction; and</li>\r\n        <li>In the event an Introduced Entity is introduced more than once, we will honor the Submission we receive earliest, unless an exclusive agreement exists between the Introduced Entity and one of the entities providing the introduction.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n    <h4 class=\"gtm-black\">B. PROCESS </h4><b>Submission (“Submission”)</b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        <!-- react-text: 254 -->To be eligible to receive the fees (“\r\n        <!-- /react-text --><b>Fee</b>\r\n        <!-- react-text: 256 -->”) described in these rules, you must accept these terms and conditions. Introductions may be submitted by completing the “Broker Introduction” form submission at\r\n        <!-- /react-text --><a href=\"https://knotel.com/brokers\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">knotel.com/brokers</a>\r\n        <!-- react-text: 258 -->and entering all required information:\r\n        <!-- /react-text -->\r\n    </p>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>Your first and last name</li>\r\n        <li>Your email address &amp; phone number</li>\r\n        <li>Introduced Entity Name</li>\r\n        <li>Name of the primary contact for the entity you are representing</li>\r\n        <li>Valid email address for the primary contact at the entity you are representing</li>\r\n        <li>Team Size (# of Seats)</li>\r\n        <li>Projected Move-In Date</li>\r\n        <li>Introduced Entity’s Knotel location of interest</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    <p>You must complete a separate Submission for each Introduced Entity. You may only complete a single Submission per potential member company that you would like to introduce. Incomplete Submissions will result in ineligibility from collecting Fees until a complete Submission is received. You further represent that the Introduced Entity has approved (verbally or in writing)