yment of any lump sum Fees will be made within seven (7) days of the Introduced Entity’s signing of a Membership Agreement for such Expansion. Monthly Fees will be paid no later than one month following each full calendar month of fully paid occupancy by the Introduced Entity’s company.</p><b>Communication</b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        <!-- react-text: 345 -->All communication regarding the amount of referral fees and the schedule of payments shall come from the Knotel Growth team. Any questions or concerns regarding these terms and the referral program should be addressed to the Knotel Growth team at\r\n        <!-- /react-text --><a href=\"mailto:brokers@knotel.com\">brokers@knotel.com</a>\r\n        <!-- react-text: 347 -->. While you may receive unofficial contact from other Knotel departments regarding your referral, please be advised that any such communication shall be considered advisory only, any information provided to you by such other team may not be correct or valid, and no determinations, especially regarding validity of a referral, made by such other team may be considered binding. The Knotel Growth team shall be responsible for the final determinations regarding all referrals made pursuant to the Knotel Referral Program.\r\n        <!-- /react-text -->\r\n    </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n    <h4 class=\"gtm-black\">D. MISCELLANEOUS</h4>\r\n    <p>\r\n        <!-- react-text: 351 -->“\r\n        <!-- /react-text --><b>Knotel</b>\r\n        <!-- react-text: 353 -->” for the purposes of these terms and conditions is Knotel, Inc., a Delaware corporation, and any of its applicable affiliates. The relevant entity that you enter into this agreement with is known in these terms and conditions as “we,” “our” or “us”. Knotel reserves the right in its sole discretion to make any determination under these rules, including, without limitation, the determination of your eligibility, a qualified introduction and the amount and payment of Fees. If Knotel determines, in it